OL,3,CMan found guilty of eight counts of
OL,4,Chistorical sexual abuse at Royal Court
OL,6,FAn 82-year-old man from Guernsey has
OL,7,Fbeen found guilty of eight counts of
OL,8,Fhistorical sexual abuse.
OL,10,FMichael Derrek Cotterill was convicted
OL,11,Ftoday (10 January) after a five-day
OL,12,Ftrial at Guernsey's Royal Court.
OL,14,FCotterill committed the crimes during
OL,15,Fthe late 1980s and early 1990s when
OL,16,Fthe victims were of primary school age.
OL,18,FThe trial saw the two victims relive
OL,19,Fwhat happened to them as young
OL,20,Fchildren.
