OL,3,CMan found guilty of eight counts of
OL,4,Chistorical sexual abuse at Royal Court
OL,6,FThe first six counts involved the
OL,7,Ffirst victim and include Cotterill
OL,8,Fasking her to touch him and herself
OL,9,Finappropriately. When she protested he
OL,10,Fwashed her mouth out with soap.
OL,12,FThe second victim told the court that
OL,13,FCotterill also asked her to touch him
OL,14,Finappropriately at his house.
OL,16,FHe also posed children in different
OL,17,Fsexual positions at his home, both in
OL,18,Fthe garden and inside the house.
