OL,3,CMan found guilty of eight counts of
OL,4,Chistorical sexual abuse at Royal Court
OL,6,FDuring the trial Cotterill
OL,7,Fconsistently said the women have been
OL,8,Flying, or falsely attributing their
OL,9,Fabuse to him.
OL,11,FAfter all the evidence was heard Judge
OL,12,FCatherine Fooks told the jurats to not
OL,13,F"let their emotions take over" when
OL,14,Fmaking a decision.
OL,16,FIt took the Jurats two hours to come
OL,17,Fto their decision and unanimously find
OL,18,FCotterill guilty on all counts.
OL,20,FCotterill will be sentenced at a later
OL,21,Fdate.
